 abuse already.  The planes (Hate more so than Fear) are especially desirable on Tuesdays, as that day of the week is more frequently a patch day.  By allowing consecutive days, you potentially allow access to a more desirable day(s) (Wednesdays are about the second most common patch days) well ahead of when non euro/asian raiders are able to attempt to reserve these days.  There has to be a better solution than this.  I want equity for those guilds, but it takes away, in potentially to large a way, from others.  Let me put it in perspective.  I have been trying to get to Hate on a Day when a certain one of the Minibosses is up, for oh say 2 to 3 months.  I have been repeatedly snafued by either 1) not getting the day  2) going on a non guild raid that was unable to get to the mob 3) going on non guild raids where the mob was not up  4) going on guild raids where the mob was not up.  Read the signups for Tuesdays/patch days... it is not unusual for the raiding group to automatically claim the staff.  The same holds true for the Golems/CT.  I will be vehemently opposed to anything that will further limit my or my guild's access to a potential patch day.  Thanks.<br>
<br>
Syrillian Manashifter<br>
59 Magician<br>
Proud Member of Enshadowed   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisplanesraids.showMessage?topicID=1663.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisplanesraids.showMessage?topicID=1694.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisplanesraids.threadControl?topicID=1687.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisplanesraids.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1687.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisplanesraids.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1687.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm48">Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisfrm56">Salutations & Congratulations <option value="brellserilisfrm33">Dreams & Diversions (Off Topic)<option value="brellserilisfrm55">Fellowship of Guilds (Guildchat)<option value="brellserilisbrellslairadminonly">Brell's Lair (Admin only)<option value="brellserilisfrm54">Tome: Sagely Advice (Newbie Q&A)<option value="brellserilismeleetalk">Tome: Races and Classes <option value="brellserilisroleplaying">Tome: History of Norrath<option value="brellserilisfrm49">Tome: Visio